---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Laitse Castle"
  description="How Nevaliste OÜ processes personal data on laitsecastle.ee, including PostHog analytics and session recording."
  locale="en"
>
  <section class="px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-prose mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-display text-hero text-warm-dark mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="font-body text-body-lg text-stone leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <p>
          This privacy policy explains how Nevaliste OÜ (Laitse Castle) collects, uses,
          and protects your personal data when you use
          <strong class="font-medium text-warm-dark">laitsecastle.ee</strong>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-subtitle text-[clamp(22px,2vw,28px)] text-warm-dark mt-10 mb-4">Data controller</h2>
        <p>
          The controller is Nevaliste OÜ.
          Contact: <a href="mailto:info@laitsecastle.ee" class="text-burgundy hover:underline">info@laitsecastle.ee</a>,
          tel <a href="tel:+37254210881" class="text-burgundy hover:underline">+372 5421 0881</a>.
          Address: Lossi tee 9, 76302 Laitse, Harju County, Estonia.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-subtitle text-[clamp(22px,2vw,28px)] text-warm-dark mt-10 mb-4">What data we process</h2>
        <p>
          <strong class="font-medium text-warm-dark">Data you send us.</strong>
          If you contact us by email or phone, we process your contact details and
          message content so we can reply and arrange a booking.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="font-medium text-warm-dark">Web analytics (PostHog, EU).</strong>
          We use PostHog’s European Union cloud (eu.i.posthog.com) to understand how
          the site is used — for example pages visited, referrer, device, and approximate
          location. By default this runs in a <em>cookieless</em> mode (data kept in
          browser memory for the session).
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="font-medium text-warm-dark">Session recording (consent only).</strong>
          If you accept cookies, PostHog may record your session (page movement, clicks)
          to help us improve the website. This uses cookies / local storage to distinguish
          visitors. Recording stays off until you consent.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-subtitle text-[clamp(22px,2vw,28px)] text-warm-dark mt-10 mb-4">Legal basis</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Enquiry contact — steps prior to a contract / legitimate interest in responding to you.</li>
          <li>Cookieless analytics — legitimate interest in understanding and improving the website.</li>
          <li>Session recording and related cookies — your consent (you may decline or change later).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-subtitle text-[clamp(22px,2vw,28px)] text-warm-dark mt-10 mb-4">Sharing</h2>
        <p>
          Analytics data is processed on our behalf by PostHog Inc. in the EU service environment.
          We do not sell your personal data. Enquiry data is not shared with third parties except
          processors needed to provide the service.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-subtitle text-[clamp(22px,2vw,28px)] text-warm-dark mt-10 mb-4">Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We keep enquiry data as long as needed to respond and arrange a booking.
          PostHog analytics retention follows our project settings (on the free plan,
          typically up to 1 year).
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-subtitle text-[clamp(22px,2vw,28px)] text-warm-dark mt-10 mb-4">Your rights</h2>
        <p>
          Under the GDPR you may request access, rectification, erasure, restriction,
          object to processing, and — where processing is based on consent — withdraw consent.
          Contact
          <a href="mailto:info@laitsecastle.ee" class="text-burgundy hover:underline">info@laitsecastle.ee</a>.
          You may also lodge a complaint with the Estonian Data Protection Inspectorate
          (Andmekaitse Inspektsioon).
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-subtitle text-[clamp(22px,2vw,28px)] text-warm-dark mt-10 mb-4">Changes</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy. The current version is always published on this page.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
